                        "description":  "Touch one object weighing 10 pounds or less and no more than 6 feet in its longest dimension; the spell marks the object and names it on a unique sapphire, then later speaking the item name and crushing the sapphire summons it to the caster\u0027s hand across any distance or plane unless another creature holds or carries it, in which case the caster learns that creature\u0027s identity and approximate location, while Dispel Magic or a similar effect on the sapphire ends the spell.",
